Shulk (Xenoblade Chronicles)
Weapon type: Unique
Crystal Color: Red
Spheres: A B D

A note on Shulk: His skills change. A lot. His base game mechanics are hard to translate perfectly into DFFOO format so I did the
best I could. His flowchart is gonna end up like Alisae's or worse

Skill 1: Back Slash
Back Slash:
 1-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Greatly increases BRV damage dealt when attacking enemies not targeting self.
 Fills Talent Gauge by 20%.
 Becomes Monado Art: Buster when [Activate Monado] is active.
Monado Art: Buster
 3-hit AoE Melee BRV+ST HP attack.
 Greatly increases BRV damage dealt to Machine-type enemies.
 Uses: 8
15cp: Replica Monado
Back Slash:
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Increases Talent Gauge amount filled  (+10%)
 +Grants Max BRV Up (40%) to self for 6 turns
Monado Art: Buster
 +Greatly improves BRV potency
 +Increases BRV damage dealt when attacking a single target (+60%)
 +Grants Max BRV Up (40%) to self for 6 turns
c.55: Back Slash Extend
 +Adds 4 uses
 +Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack+ when [Activate Monado] is not active
 +Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack++ when [Activate Monado] is active
Back Slash:
 +Becomes a 4-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
Monado Art: Buster
 +Becomes a 6-hit AoE Melee+ST HP attack
 +Greatly increases total BRV potency
 +Deals 50% splash HP damage to non-targets
 +Allows for 180% Stolen BRV overflow

Talent Gauge:
An overhead gauge that fills much like an EX recast gauge.
Once Talent Gauge reaches 100%, turns into special effect [Activate Monado] for 3 turns.
Once [Activate Monado]'s duration reaches 0, Talent Gauge returns to 0%.
[Activate Monado]: Critical Hit Rate Up (100%), Critical Hit Damage Up (100%)
                   All BRV damage ignores DEF
BRV Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV attack
BRV Attack++: 3-hit Melee BRV attack
              Greatly increases BRV damage dealt to Machine-type enemies

Skill 2: Stream Edge
Stream Edge: 
 Breaks all enemies, if not already Broken.
 AoE Melee HP attack.
 Deals 100% HP damage to all enemies.
 Fills Talent Gauge by 50%.
 Becomes Monado Art: Cyclone when [Activate Monado] is active.
Monado Art: Cyclone
 2-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Deals 100% HP damage to all enemies.
 Greatly increases BRV damage dealt to Machine-type enemies.
 Uses: 3
35cp: Monado Agni
Stream Edge:
 +Multiply own BRV by 1.3 before HP damage (Occurs before BRV hits if c60 passive is equipped)
Monado Art: Cyclone
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Reduces enemy BRV to 0 before BRV hits (no effect if enemy is Broken)
c.60: Stream Edge Extend
 +Adds 2 uses
 +Turns HP Attack to HP Attack+ when [Activate Monado] is not active
 +Turns HP Attack to HP Attack++ when [Activate Monado] is active
Stream Edge:
 +Becomes a 4-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
 +Resets enemy Break status before Breaking enemies
Monado Art: Cyclone
 +Becomes a 5-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
 
HP Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
HP Attack++: 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
             Greatly increases BRV damage dealt to Machine-type enemies
 
EX: Monado
 +Equips EX ability Shaker Edge
Shaker Edge:
 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow.
 Grants [Shadow Eye] to self for 2 turns after use.
 Fills Talent Gauge by 20%.
 Becomes Monado Art: Purge when [Activate Monado] is active.
Monado Art: Purge
 4-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Greatly increases BRV damage dealt to Machine-type enemies.
 Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow.
 Inflicts [Aura Seal] on target for 2 turns.
 Grants [Vision] to self for 2 turns.
Recast: Slightly Slow
  -LB1: Slightly increases BRV damage dealt (+10%)
  -LB2: Increases Recast speed by 20%
  -LB3: Increases party's SPD (+20%) when [Activate Monado] is active
 EX+: Greatly increases BRV potency of Shaker Edge/Monado Art: Purge
      Slightly increases 
  -LB1: Increases own ATK (60%) and Max BRV (50%)
  -LB2: Start Quest with 6 turns Max BRV Up (40%) and 20% Talent Gauge fill
  -LB3: Increases own Stolen BRV overflow limit for all attacks (+30%)
       Shaker Edge:
        +Becomes a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered twice
        +Tremedously increases BRV potency
        +Gain BRV based on (30% of) HP damage dealt after both HP attacks
        +Deals 20% total splash HP damage to non-targets
       Monado Art: Purge:
        +Becomes a 4-hit Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered twice
        +Tremendously increases BRV potency
        +Gain BRV based on (30% of) HP damage dealt after both HP attacks
        +Deals 20% total splash HP damage to non-targets

[Shadow Eye]: ATK Up (50%)
              Prevents enemies from targeting self
[Aura Seal]: Prevents enemies from affecting self or player party with aura effects.
[Vision]: Evasion Rate Up (50%)
          When self or an ally is about to take fatal damage, Shulk intercepts with a free turn in which his skills change
           *During this turn, Shulk cannot use EX, LD, c65 or CA abilities.
           *Does not increase turn count. Increases Friend Support, Summon, and Burst phase turn count.
Light Heal: Replaces BRV Attack.
            Heals an ally for 15% of their Max HP.
Monado Art: Shield: Replaces HP Attack.
                    Grants [Monado Shield] to all allies for 1 turn.
Monado Art: Speed: Replaces Back Slash/Monado Art: Buster.
                   Does not consume skill usage.
                   Grants [Monado Speed] to one ally for 1 turn.
Monado Art: Armor: Replaces Stream Edge/Monado Art: Cyclone.
                   Does not consume skill usage.
                   Grants [Monado Armor] to all allies for 1 turn.
[Monado Shield]: Blocks HP damage based on own INT BRV (50%).
[Monado Speed]: Evasion Rate Up (90%)
[Monado Armor]: PHY Damage Reduction (60%)
                MAG Damage Reduction (60%)

LD: Monado REX
+Equips LD ability Monado Art: Eater
 3-hit AoE Melee BRV+ST HP attack, triggered twice.
 Gain BRV based on (20% of) HP damage dealt after both HP attacks.
 Greatly increases BRV damage dealt to Machine-type enemies.
 Deals 50% splash HP damage to non-targets.
 Dispels all enemy buffs, including framed buffs.
 Fills Talent Gauge to 100% and activates [Activate Monado] before BRV hits.
 Inflicts [Bleed] on all targets for 6 turns.
 Uses: 2
  -LB1: Raises party's ATK, Max BRV by 20%
        Increases BRV damage dealt (+10%)
  -LB2: Raises party's ATK, Max BRV by 20%
        Improves the effects of [Bleed] (+30%)
  -LB3: Raises party's ATK, Max BRV by 20%
        Adds +1 use
  
[Bleed]: Poison (20% target Max BRV)
         Deals HP damage by 50% of Attack (will not reduce HP below 1)
         
BT: Monado II
+Equips Burst ability Monado Unbound
 12-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
 Deals 80% splash HP damage to non-targets
 Greatly increases BRV damage dealt to Machine-type enemies

Maximum BRV damage limit +150% (up to 24997)
Maximum obtainable BRV & HP damage limit +200% (up to 299997)

BURST Effect (5 turns, party-wide)
• BRV damage dealt +50%
• All BRV damage ignores DEF
• Maximum BRV damage limit +20% (up to 11998)
• Stolen BRV overflow limit +30%
* Same character's BURST effects do not stack
BT Theme: You Will Know Our Names
